{"tid":1018681,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大摩指股市上行空間有限 建議即時離場","createTime":"2019-02-12T11:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T14:28:05.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bc5a7c6f2fdeed4abe9d5e60e850964235f8b3d4","tid":1018681,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"2019/01/29 14:14<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n摩根士丹利首席股票策略師Mike Wilson表示，縱使股市仍有一些上升空間，投資者目前應立即撤出股市。他形容去年平安夜以來的股市反彈如同坐上狂牛背上，指目前已坐在牛背8秒鐘，已接近要跳下來的時候，並警告牛有時候是危險的動物。<br />\n<br />\nWilson又指，自去年12月股市急跌以來，市場活動短促而波動，即使沽售信號不如標普500指數在2,900點時那麼清晰，投資者亦是時候考慮另覓其他投資，並稱目前在可見時間內難以看到上行空間。<br />\n<br />\n他亦表示，美股雙位數的盈利增長是受到低稅及低預期所推動，導致未來對照時更難表現理想，預期今年首三季企業每股盈利只會按年增長1.3%至3.5%。(fc/t)"},{"pid":"af04efaf0548067d9811d873ee6383ae68b9346c","tid":1018681,"uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"大摩真係好仆街，自私食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e57773236d1048ced4a35e706a887cbfae9bb55","tid":1018681,"uid":162511,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"af04efaf0548067d9811d873ee6383ae68b9346c","tid":1018681,"uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"大摩真係好仆街，自私食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"唔夠你仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa91fa93360995a1f9c14b0d8fb389e284fec1d8","tid":1018681,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"1月29號低位計已經升左800點上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98477dec13b681077fe1f46231901acd9d4ec52a","tid":1018681,"uid":227275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"